        <bioghist id="ref3">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>Joseph Mandrillon was a French businessman and writer. He was elected to the American Philosophical Society in 1785.</p>
        </bioghist>
        <odd id="ref12">
            <head>Early American History Note</head>
            <p>This small leather bound volume contains an essay by APS member Joseph Mandrillon. The essay discusses the discovery of America, early exploration, and colonization. It is written in French. Mandrillon was a Frenchman who became a member in 1785. This volume was also printed.</p>
